# Environment
.env
cc-history-api.md

# MCPB bundle build outputs — mcpb/manifest.json is committed as the
# source-of-truth manifest; the bundled binary and the packaged .mcpb
# archive are reproducible from `cargo build --release` plus the bundling
# step, and are kept out of git history to avoid bloat
mcpb/bin/
mcpb/*.mcpb
